#: ../../source/QA.rst:4
msgid "Q&A"
msgstr "问答"

#: ../../source/QA.rst
msgid "Q: How can I get the add-on?"
msgstr "问：我如何获取插件？"

#: ../../source/QA.rst:8
msgid ""
"You can download the add-on ``.zip`` file directly from the "
"|github_releases| page."
msgstr "你可以直接从 |github_releases| 页面下载插件的 ``.zip`` 文件。"

#: ../../source/QA.rst
msgid "Q: Which versions of Blender are supported?"
msgstr "问：插件支持哪些版本的 Blender？"

#: ../../source/QA.rst:28
msgid "The **minimum supported version** is **Blender 4.2 LTS**."
msgstr "插件 **最低支持版本** 为 **Blender 4.2 LTS**。"

#: ../../source/QA.rst:30
msgid ""
"The add-on is developed and tested primarily on Blender 4.2. Newer "
"versions of Blender ( such as **Blender 4.5** ) may also work, but they "
"have not been fully tested yet."
msgstr "该插件主要在 Blender 4.2 上开发和测试。更高版本的 Blender（如 **Blender 4.5**）也可能可用，但尚未经过完整测试。"

#: ../../source/QA.rst
msgid "Q: What license does the add-on use?"
msgstr "问：插件使用什么许可证？"

#: ../../source/QA.rst:35
msgid ""
"The add-on is released under the |GPLv3| license. You are free to use, "
"modify, and redistribute the add-on, provided that you comply with the "
"terms of the |GPLv3| license."
msgstr "该插件采用 |GPLv3| 许可证发布。你可以自由使用、修改和重新分发插件，但需遵守 |GPLv3| 许可证条款。"

#: ../../source/QA.rst
msgid "Q: How to get the MMD add-on?"
msgstr "问：如何获取 MMD 插件？"

#: ../../source/QA.rst:62
msgid "The **MMD Tools** can be downloaded from |MMD_Tools|."
msgstr "可以从 |MMD_Tools| 下载 **MMD Tools** 插件。"

#: ../../source/QA.rst
msgid "Q: How can I obtain MMD models for reference?"
msgstr "问：如何获取 MMD 模型以供参考？"

#: ../../source/QA.rst:72
msgid "Many MMD models can be found online."
msgstr "你可以在网上找到许多 MMD 模型。"

#: ../../source/QA.rst:74
msgid ""
"For example, You can visit the |bilibili_link| website and search for "
"*绝区零UP主激励计划*. On the corresponding page, locate the *模型下载* section and "
"click *下载模型* to obtain the latest MMD character models from the game "
"*Zenless Zone Zero*."
msgstr ""
"例如，你可以访问 |bilibili_link| 网站，搜索“*绝区零UP主激励计划*”。在对应页面找到 *模型下载* 区域，点击 "
"*下载模型*，即可获取游戏 *绝区零* 的最新 MMD 角色模型。"

#: ../../source/QA.rst
msgid "Q: Where can I report bugs or request new features?"
msgstr "问：我可以在哪里提交 Bug 或请求新功能？"

#: ../../source/QA.rst:84
msgid "Bugs and feature requests can be reported via |github_issues|."
msgstr "你可以通过 |github_issues| 提交 Bug 和功能请求。"

